thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by GUY

author: GUY
title: GUY
text:
We arrived with a wrong reservation with RentalCar. At first, we did not find the renter witch was down town in Adelaide and then after, was not abble to bring us at the airport in time to catch our plane early.
We had to find a car immediatly at the airport. "Enterprise" found us the right car at the right moment (go & return) at the right place & the right fee
